{"id": 1781, "genre": 1000, "title": "你是哪一种测评贴使用者？", "description": "现在的测评贴都穷极详尽，你会看哪一种？关注什么？（题图来自：Vimeo）", "record_count": 4727, "comment_count": 14, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170704101035Oz9ZBcrliNeIKkRt.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-18T17:00:03Z", "questions": [{"id": 2552, "title": "你是哪一种测评贴使用者？", "content": "你是哪一种测评贴使用者？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 218804, "content": "科学探究型，会仔细看测评贴里的实验数据，使用的仪器，操作方法", "image": "img/option/option/20170704101124TStgc47GrqMIiVsb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 218805, "content": "直奔主题型，根本不看参数，直接拉到推荐购买的list里看推荐购买的单品top3", "image": "img/option/option/20170704101151ZigSnUMcIYlrqmdX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 218806, "content": "real刚需型，一般不看，只会在买自己不懂的产品的时候参考", "image": "img/option/option/20170704101216d0E5YMVpL3jKTu6B.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 218807, "content": "即使不买也要看测评型，不为购物，只为了解世界", "image": "img/option/option/20170704101242kJd1QVmE62wtc7vo.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 218808, "content": "新闻导向型，比如看到有哪家著名企业的产品有大问题的测评，会去看爆料", "image": "img/option/option/20170704101300gC4LIjprNwYu3amQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 218810, "content": "测评撰写者本人，新产品试用者总会迫不及待想写下使用体验", "image": "img/option/option/20170704101407g7uqARWL0PzbpQ5t.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 218811, "content": "根本不看型，“这破玩意儿也值得测评吗”型，觉得有点小题大做", "image": "img/option/option/20170704101424mQYe8ZD21alSBIuc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}